divs: Sighting DetailsWhile Driving On I-5 North Bound,Just Before The Nisqually Exit, Something Caught My Attention.,I Observed A Grey Oval Shaped Object Streek Across The Freeway.It Was Approximatly,100-Ft Long,25-Ft High,And There Where No Beacon Lights On It.It's Speed Was Very Fast,When I First Noticed It,It Was Flying Directly In The Middle Of(Across)The Freeway,About 250-Ft In The Air.It Only Took Around 5-Seconds Before It Dissapered Behind A Hill,To The North.I Really Don't Know What It Was.When I Exited Off The Freeway,At The Nisqually Exit,I Noticed An Army Helicopter Flying In The Area.,Not Unusual,Do To Fort Lewis To The East.
